@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : getFleetStatus()
activate System

note right of System: The system fetches all fleet aircraft,\ngroups them by operational status,\nand computes the dashboard totals.

System --> ATCC : returns fleet total and status counts
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml